---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import DataField from '../components/DataField.astro';
---

<Layout title="vesl">
  <DataField />
  <main>
    <nav>
      <div class="nav-inner">
        <a href="/" class="logo">
          <img src="/logo.svg" alt="vesl" class="logo-mark" />
        </a>
        <div class="nav-links">
          <a href="https://docs.zkvesl.org">docs</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/zkVesl/vesl">github</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <h1><img src="/vesl_horizontal_alpha.svg" alt="vesl" class="hero-logo" /></h1>
        <p class="tagline">
          Verifiable Execution and Settlement Layer
        </p>
        <p class="sub">
          Build on infrastructure where every computation is provable and every state transition is verified. No trust required.
        </p>
        <div class="cta">
          <a href="https://docs.zkvesl.org" class="btn primary">Get started</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/zkVesl/vesl" class="btn secondary">View source</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="scroll-hint" aria-hidden="true">&#8595;</div>
    </section>

    <!-- CARD 1 -->
    <section class="card" id="card-1">
      <pre class="card-code" aria-hidden="true">addr   00 01 02 03 04 05 06 07   08 09 0a 0b 0c 0d 0e 0f
0000   76 65 73 6c 2e 70 72 6f   6f 66 2e 76 65 72 69 66
0010   69 65 64 00 73 74 61 74   65 2e 63 6f 6d 6d 69 74
0020   00 6e 6f 63 6b 2e 65 78   65 63 00 64 65 74 65 72
0030   6d 69 6e 69 73 74 69 63   00 76 65 72 69 66 69 61
0040   62 6c 65 2e 62 79 2e 64   65 66 61 75 6c 74 00 00
0050   63 6f 6d 6d 69 74 6d 65   6e 74 2e 68 61 73 68 00
0060   70 72 6f 6f 66 2e 76 61   6c 69 64 00 00 00 00 00</pre>
      <div class="card-inner">
        <span class="card-number">01</span>
        <h2>verifiable by default</h2>
        <div class="card-rule"></div>
        <p>
          ::  Every operation produces a cryptographic proof. Not as an add-on. Not as a premium feature. As the foundation. If it ran, you can verify it. If you can't verify it, it didn't run.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CARD 2 -->
    <section class="card" id="card-2">
      <pre class="card-code" aria-hidden="true">+------------------------------------------+
|  nock formula  [8 [1 0] 8 [1 6 [5 [0 7] |
|                [4 0 6]] [0 6] 9 2 [0 2]  |
|                [4 0 6] 0 7]              |
|  subject       [42 0]                    |
|  product       42                        |
|  verified      true                      |
|  cycles        7                         |
+------------------------------------------+
|  ::  decrement gate                      |
|  |=  a=@                                 |
|  =|  i=0                                 |
|  ?:  =(i a)  i                           |
|  $(i +(i))                               |
+------------------------------------------+</pre>
      <div class="card-inner">
        <span class="card-number">02</span>
        <h2>nockchain native</h2>
        <div class="card-rule"></div>
        <p>
          ::  Nock is a minimal, deterministic virtual machine. Same input, same output, every time. Your application logic compiles down to something a machine can prove and anyone can verify. No opaque runtimes. No trust assumptions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CARD 3 -->
    <section class="card" id="card-3">
      <pre class="card-code" aria-hidden="true">
  ::  hoon
  |=  [n=@ud]
  ^-  @ud
  ?:  =(n 0)  1
  (mul n $(n (dec n)))

  ::  what it actually says
  fn factorial(n: uint) -> uint {'{'}
    if n == 0 {'{'} return 1 {'}'}
    n * factorial(n - 1)
  {'}'}</pre>
      <div class="card-inner">
        <span class="card-number">03</span>
        <h2>alien language, human interface</h2>
        <div class="card-rule"></div>
        <p>
          ::  Hoon compiles to Nock. Dense, correct, and nearly impossible to read unless you've called it home for years. Vesl handles the Hoon so you don't have to — you write Rust, Vesl compiles it down to something the machine can prove, and humans can read.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CARD 4 -->
    <section class="card" id="card-4">
      <pre class="card-code" aria-hidden="true">
  on-chain
  └─ settle proof         ✓  1 txn

  off-chain (vesl)
  ├─ execute              ✓  nock
  ├─ prove                ✓  zk
  └─ state transition     ✓  verified

  chain sees: proof
  chain does: verify
  chain cost: constant</pre>
      <div class="card-inner">
        <span class="card-number">04</span>
        <h2>this is how nockchain scales</h2>
        <div class="card-rule"></div>
        <p>
          ::  Move computation off-chain. Prove it happened correctly. Only the proof settles. The chain never re-executes your logic — it just verifies. Complexity grows off-chain; on-chain cost stays constant.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <footer>
      <div class="footer-inner">
        <div class="footer-links">
          <a href="https://docs.zkvesl.org">docs</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/zkVesl/vesl">github</a>
        </div>
        <p class="sigil">~</p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </main>

  <div class="nockchain-bar">
    :: BUILT ON NOCKCHAIN ::
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    width: 100%;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }

  .nav-inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .logo {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .logo:hover { text-decoration: none; }

  .logo-mark {
    height: 28px;
    width: auto;
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .nav-links a {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .nav-links a:hover {
    color: var(--fg);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    max-width: 720px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  h1 {
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .hero-logo {
    height: clamp(2.2rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
    width: auto;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--fg);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .nockchain-bar {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 100%;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .sub {
    color: #999;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 0.65rem 1.8rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .btn:hover { text-decoration: none; }

  .btn.primary {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--bg);
  }

  .btn.primary:hover {
    background: #00dd8a;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .btn.secondary {
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .btn.secondary:hover {
    border-color: rgba(214, 214, 214, 0.2);
    color: var(--fg);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .scroll-hint {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 2.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    animation: pulse 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.2; transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { opacity: 0.6; transform: translateY(5px); }
  }

  /* CONTENT LAYER — sits above canvas */
  main {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  /* CARDS */
  .card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 4rem;
    padding: 4rem 8%;
    position: relative;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }

  .card-code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--accent);
    opacity: 0.55;
    white-space: pre;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 255, 163, 0.25);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 255, 163, 0.08), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 50%, rgba(0, 255, 163, 0.08));
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  .card-inner {
    max-width: 520px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .card-number {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .card h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--fg);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }

  .card-rule {
    width: 40px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  .card p {
    color: #888;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* Even cards reverse: code left, text right */
  #card-2, #card-4 { flex-direction: row-reverse; }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .footer-inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .footer-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .footer-links a {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .footer-links a:hover {
    color: var(--fg);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .sigil {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  /* MOBILE */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .card {
      flex-direction: column !important;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      gap: 2rem;
      min-height: auto;
    }

    .card-code {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .footer-inner {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
